Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.75,0:02:27.87,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友情爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:30.79,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与想象中相反的单纯内里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:33.75,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都让那稚嫩的自我意识
